metadata.title: Sugar Vine Art Large 10.5" Wall Clock Decorative Round Wall Clock Home Decor Novelty Clock Deck ON The Ocean Beach
features: This is a printed image, from a laser printer, adhered onto a clock base. This is a USA Quartz clock movement (Guaranteed 2 yrs). This product uses an AA battery which is not included. This is not actual wood.

This is a QUIET almost SILENT non ticking clock. You have to place it close to your ear to hear it. Large 10.5" Open Face Clock NO COVER OR FRAME. It has large 4.5" metal hands (not plastic). Each clock is handmade to order.
This clock is handmade in the USA. It is an indoor decorative clock covered by a laser printed paper print with no plastic frame, and no glass cover. This is not waterproof.

The printed face can be personalized free if you choose. You will just need to send a message through the message system. There are larger 15.5” clocks in the shop if you are looking for a larger size clock. Not all designs come in the 15.5” size.

This is only recommended for indoor use. This is not an outdoor clock. There is a built-in hanger on the back of the clock movement for easy hanging. The high resolution image is printed using a large format professional laser jet printer producing sharp pictures with vivid colors.
description: This is not a wood clock.
This is an image custom printed onto an OPEN FACE CLOCK with no cover over the top. This clock does not need a frame.
It is a rigid thick hard base clock face with a quartz clock movement mounted on the back. There is a built-in hanger on the back of the clock movement for easy hanging.

Each clock in the shop is handmade to order. This is not a store bought plastic clock and the face is almost twice the size of competitors. All parts including the quartz clock movement are made in the USA.
Large 10.5" Open face means no cover or frame.
Quartz clock movement made in USA, Guaranteed 2 yrs, AA battery not included.
Recommended for indoor use not outdoor.

The printed face can be personalized free if you choose. You will just need to send me a message through the message system. The high resolution image is printed using a large format professional laser jet printer producing sharp pictures with vivid colors. This is NOT meant to be an outdoor clock. Each clock is made to order. Printing and assembling will take 2 business days to process. You should receive your clock within 7 business days after payment.
